    "Therefore, it is worthwhile for us to reassess STS theory and its implications for HCAI practice from a broader sociotechnical perspective, further enabling HCAI in practice and maximizing its contributions.",
    "EMERGING CHALLENGES TO TRADITIONAL STS THEORY A.",
    "New sociotechnical characteristics in AISTS theory was developed in the 1950s, and since then, the focus of STS research has been too narrow, there are new contexts and problems that could benefit substantially from STS thinking [34].",
